Package: emulate
Title: Target Trial Emulation via Sequential Trials
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2026-03-20
Authors@R: person("Timothy P", "Copeland", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "timothy.copeland@ki.se")
Author: Timothy P Copeland [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Timothy P Copeland <timothy.copeland@ki.se>
Description: Implements the sequential trials framework (Hernan & Robins 2016)
    for target trial emulation from observational data. Provides a pipeline for
    data preparation, validation, clone-censor-weight expansion, inverse
    probability weighting, pooled logistic regression / Cox PH fitting,
    G-formula marginal predictions with Monte Carlo confidence intervals,
    weight diagnostics, and publication-quality output. Produces numerically
    equivalent results to the Stata 'emulate' package.
